d keep your small minded, pathetic, class envying comments to yourself.<br><br>Oh, and that's coming from an Iksar Shaman who can't wear a fookin JBB.<br><br>I NEVER go oom btw.<br>&nbsp;<br>Do you think that's air your breathing? Hmm.....</td></tr>
